---
title: Lobster and Shrimp Ravioli in Rose Sauce with Mushrooms, Pine Nuts and Garlic Bread
description: This rose cream sauce pairs perfectly with umami-rich mushrooms and subtly sweet lobster and shrimp. We've brought tarragon along for the ride to add freshness, while toasted pine nuts add nuttiness and crunch. You won't want to lose any of the luscious sauce, so there's even garlic bread to mop it all up!
